data.description: This beautifully remodeled, move-in-ready home offers convenience to all that Huntsville has to offer. Featuring LVP and waterproof bamboo flooring throughout, a kitchen with a lovely tile backsplash and butcher block counters, and a fully fenced back yard with a covered patio and separate garden area. The deep 1-car garage provides ample storage space for your belongings and vehicle. Mortgage is assumable!
